item.title: Music
item.dc:creator: @The_Un-Named The Un-Named
item.description:
@The_Un-Named wrote:

hm where to start, in order of preference:

nwobhm, nwoshm (new wave of british/swedish heavy metal)
classic/traditional heavy metal
black, death, folk, progressive, thrash metal
some power and speed metal bands can be good but certainly are not my favourite

general idea of other genre:
heavy rock leading up to metal, see: riot
some jazz but preferably jazz fusion metal, see: atheist and cynic, hell, on the subject of atheist: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K4mbeVHtzwE
some classical music, can be love or hate, generally if there’s a metal fusion I’ll tend to lean to that more, see: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4w90MBg7JoA although the original night on a bald mountain is amazing
